PrecisAppointment of SONIA GAAL, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a member of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and deemed that she be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective August 2, 1999.
